<tr>
<td>Application for School of Computing Second Major and Minor Programmes for enrollment in Semester 2, AY25/26</td>
<td>
<p>Application period:<strong>&nbsp;14 Nov 2025, 9AM to 30 Nov 2025, 11.59PM</strong></p>
<p>All applications must be submitted via the Academic Plan Declaration and Application (APAD) in <strong><a href="https://myedurec.nus.edu.sg/psp/cs90prd/?cmd=login&amp;languageCd=ENG&amp;" target="_blank" rel="noopener">EduRec</a>.</strong></p>
<p>To find out how to register, you can click&nbsp;<a href="https://www.comp.nus.edu.sg/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/UserGuide-Academic_Plan_Application.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here&nbsp;</a>for the User guide.</p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Application for Double Degree Programmes for School of Computing students, for enrollment in Semester 2, AY25/26</td>
<td>
