<p>Application procedure: &lt;https://socug.comp.nus.edu.sg&gt;;&nbsp;<span style="font-family: inherit;font-style: inherit;font-weight: inherit">Please file an RT under Double Degree queue with the subject heading &#8220;DDP Application for Semester 2, AY25/26&#8221;,&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: inherit;font-size: inherit;font-style: inherit;font-weight: inherit">stating your student number, and DDP programme of interest (hons/non-hons).&nbsp;</span>Please complete the application form (complete study plan) for the eligible cohorts.<span style="font-family: inherit;font-size: inherit;font-style: inherit;font-weight: inherit">&nbsp;<br><br>If you are non SoC student, please apply through your home DDP administrator, by your home faculty deadline.</span></p>
